(2220, 742, 'Liberia', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">\n	When booking a flight for Liberia, it&rsquo;s worth making sure you&rsquo;re going to the right one. As well as being a country in West Africa, Liberia is also the capital and largest city of the Guancaste province of Costa Rica.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\n	&lsquo;The White City&rsquo;, as Liberia is known, is famous for its uniquely ice-white buildings topped by red tiled roofs, a product of the local white gravel used to build much of the city. Broad avenues run across the town, traversing the Iglesia de la Agonia, the city&rsquo;s oldest church to the many ranches surrounding the city, a throwback to its cowboy roots. Once, Liberia&rsquo;s beautifully lush Guancaste trees provided a shady resting place for weary travellers; now Costa Rica&rsquo;s oldest town is an important tourist hub, especially for those on their way to the beaches of the nearby pacific coast. Liberia travel guides show it is also a top destination for its Volcanic National Park, the Rincon de le Vieja where visitors can see the bubbling hot springs, volcanic rivers and waterfalls from the safety of hiking trails.&nbsp;</p>\n', 1, 0, 47, '10.64', '-85.45', 'liberia', 0, 1),
