(5973, 2021, 'Da Lat', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">\n	With near perfect weather all year round DaLat is a popular tourist draw for thousands of local and international visitors every year. This &ldquo;City of Eternal Spring&rdquo; has a distinct French feel with mist covering its valleys and romance in the air. Nature has been generous in endowing Dalat with waterfalls and lakes and endless green mountains, all coming together to give the city its picture postcard like beauty. Immerse yourself in this scenic splendour with hiking trails, rafting adventures, mountain climbing, waterfall visits, and plenty of photo opportunities. Take a step back in time with your Dalat Tour Guide to see the city&rsquo;s rich culture and heritage with a visit to the summer palaces of the last Vietnam Emperor Bao Dai. Don&rsquo;t miss out on a visit to the Flower Garden or the cable car ride to the Thien Vien Truc Lam Monastery. Whether you are looking for nature exploration, cultural experiences, or a romantic getaway, go to DaLat to discover it has it all and more!</p>\n', 1, 0, 228, '11.96', '108.44', 'da-lat', 0, 1),
